{"tid":1313117,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬路彈匣誰屬？01片段揭無戴證便衣警佩槍失彈匣","createTime":"2019-07-13T16:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T16:29:21.000Z","uid":262201,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"861a4d56dc8f2efa2757f5f6a30a9ce54a2cf643","tid":1313117,"uid":262201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:25:12.000Z","msg":"光復上水遊行結束後，便演變為警民衝突，新運路一段戰火連連，其間香港01記者在新運路及智昌路交界路面發現一個彈匣，相信有警員遺下。香港01記者其後翻查片段，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">發現彈匣是屬於一名沒有配戴委任證的便衣警員所有</span></span>，下午5時49分，他與三名便衣警因沒有出示委任證被示威者包圍，示威者向其後方投擲鐵欄，他衝前向示威者揮警棍，混亂間跌了彈匣。01片段可見其佩槍由有彈匣變成空空如也，而馬路上亦有疑似黑色長條型物件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/351652/%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4-%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E5%BD%88%E5%8C%A3%E8%AA%B0%E5%B1%AC-01%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E6%8F%AD%E7%84%A1%E6%88%B4%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6%E4%BD%A9%E6%A7%8D%E5%A4%B1%E5%BD%88%E5%8C%A3?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=realism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F351652%2F%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%258C%25A3%25E8%25AA%25B0%25E5%25B1%25AC-01%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2588%25B4%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E6%25A7%258D%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%258C%25A3%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Drealism&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL0tjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=ecb73beb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/351652/%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4-%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E5%BD%88%E5%8C%A3%E8%AA%B0%E5%B1%AC-01%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E6%8F%AD%E7%84%A1%E6%88%B4%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6%E4%BD%A9%E6%A7%8D%E5%A4%B1%E5%BD%88%E5%8C%A3?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campa